    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has significant scratches, dents, and paint damage across multiple panels. The interior shows heavy wear including torn or heavily soiled upholstery, damaged trim, and worn surfaces throughout. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention. Suitable for buyers prepared to invest in repairs or looking for parts.",
